message:
Hey Crutons! So... you're looking for a fun church service midday on Friday for Good Friday? Wouldn't it be fun to go to a midday church service!?!?? Well, you can! Hope Community Church, Bethlehem Baptist, Augustana, Bethesda, and a few other neighboring churches are partnering to do a Good Neighbor Fellowship/Good Friday service at Bethlehem Baptist (2 blocks down from Hope)! It'll be this Friday from noon to 1pm. I'll be going and can pick people up if need be! Let me know! I have 3 spots available! (Ian Dorney, you have one already!) 

ALSO, if anyone wants rides to the Hope CC Good Friday service, I can provide those as well! Hope has a 6pm and an 8pm service and I'll be at both. 

Let me know for any and all services you want/need a ride to! :)
